Title: Wellborn 2R Premium Beef Bundle - Filet Mignons, Sirloin Steaks, Flat Iron Steaks and Ground Beef USDA Prime Texas Beef
Items: WELLBORN 2R RANCH - We are Wellborn 2R Ranch – a historic ranch in Henrietta, Texas, located two hours northwest of Dallas. Cattle have been grazing our ranges since the 1870s along with generations of families and cowboys that have tended to them. The combination of optimal cattle growing land and the accumulation of 150 years of experience allows us to produce the best, all-natural Black Angus beef you can buy  , WHATS IN THE BUNDLE - A starter kit with some of our most popular cuts: 2x Sirloin Steaks (8 oz) 2x Tenderloin Filets (5-6 oz) 2x Flat Iron Steak (7-8 oz) 2x Ground Beef (1 lb pkg)  , 2x Sirloin Steaks (8 oz) Our high choice or prime grade all-natural Angus Sirloin Steaks are the best bargains of the whole beef! Dense marbling and incredible flavor. This Black Angus beef is raised the old-fashioned way on the pastures and then grain-finished. Its firm texture makes an exceptional meal and is ideal for broiling, pan-searing, or grilling.  , 2x Tenderloin Filets (5-6 oz) All-natural Angus tenderloin steaks, also known as filet mignons, are the leanest cuts available, yet marbled enough to deliver full flavor. Each filet is hand-cut by our artisan butcher and slowly wet-aged for the ultimate tenderness and rich, buttery flavor profile. This steak also meets government guidelines for lean.  , 2x Flat Iron Steak (7-8 oz) Our Flat Iron is a well-marbled savory 8 oz. steak that remains sufficiently lean. Originating from the Top Blade Roast, our cutting method produces a cut of beef ranked by many steak enthusiasts second only to the tenderloin for tenderness. Flat Iron steaks are great on the grill, broiled in the oven, or pan-seared in a skillet.  , Our hamburger is fantastic and one of our best sellers. It is made from the same stock of beef that we cut our prime and high choice steaks from. We think you are going to love it as much as all of our other customers do. We can’t emphasize enough how much better it is than what you get at the store, which comes from a variety of sources and you just don’t know what you are getting.
